headline: Otis’s (NYSE:OTIS) Q3 Sales Top Estimates
summary: Elevator manufacturer Otis (NYSE:OTIS) beat Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q3 CY2025, with sales up 4% year on year to $3.69 billion. The company expects the full year’s revenue to be around $14.55 billion, close to analysts’ estimates. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.05 per share was 4.7% above analysts’ consensus estimates.

headline: OTIS REPORTS THIRD QUARTER 2025 RESULTS
summary: Otis Worldwide Corporation (NYSE:OTIS) reported third quarter 2025 net sales of $3.7 billion with organic sales up 2% versus the prior year. GAAP earnings per share (EPS) decreased 29% to $0.95 and adjusted EPS increased 9% to $1.05.
